Summary: It's ok. . . but I like Eight O'Clock better
text:
This coffee is really ok. . . I know what to expect with Starbucks. I know what I don't like . . and what I do like . . . . But I have to say, especially for the cost, I really like Eight O'Clock better. If you really want more vanilla flavor, I think you should give it a try.

Eight O'Clock Coffee, French Vanilla Ground, 11-Ounce Bags (Pack of 4)
